title: Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
